<h1 style="font-size:24px; line-height:28px; font-weight:bold;display:inline;">山西长治落马市长情妇贪污6359万被判死缓 <a onclick="addbookmark(window.location,'山西长治落马市长情妇贪污6359万被判死缓')" style="cursor:pointer;"><img src="/images/dvbbs0/vcopyt.gif" align="absmiddle" /></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="#" id="bbs_go_hwact" style="display:none;" target="_blank"><img src="http://bbs.voc.com.cn/images/bbs_hwact.gif" /></a></h1>
    <br /><br /><span style="font-size:14px;dispaly:block;"><font color="gray">haitun 发表在</font> <a href="forum-68-1.html">新闻聚焦</a> <font color="gray">华声论坛 http://bbs.voc.com.cn/forum-68-1.html</font></span>

